Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌  是我们学校的学生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架了吗  真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这个世界里时间没有动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真是悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}入此门者  当抛弃一切希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:03:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位同学来到小生广原雪子担当部长的考现学部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考现学就是以现代社会的森罗万象为对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做调查  研究的学问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说就是考古学的现代版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我已经听了好几遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  考现学部终于盼来了新部员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是两名女生和一名男生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的  姐姐在7年前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赤夜里看到的肯定是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡思乱想太多比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经和大家聚到一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴啊  认识了好多伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子真厉害啊  在赤夜中一个人生存下来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  雪子也有特别的能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一生气就很可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子总是这么活泼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为也就只有这点优点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  在哪跟谁打架能伤成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的出勤快不够了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近总是旷课  还想不想升学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦  你这嫁不出去的缺男人婆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久  你的对女性不出手主义让我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  给我站住贤久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士称呼我们为「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要回答即将消失的「碎片」们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「碎片」是指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及「碎片」还有几人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还知道一个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赤夜刚开始那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被个好像正义的伙伴一样的人救了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子同学  你也认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「她」  是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说得出口啊  那个世界的事  还有这能力的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  决定了  今天的活动就是寻找那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定了那就事不宜迟  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久  逃哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然撞进来干什么  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是正义的伙伴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜妹  又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学  搜查活动结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人吃惊啊  能看到黑月的人竟然有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像叫臯月来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什么能力都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你这样还能活到今天啊  真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别生气嘛  我是在夸奖你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来点薯条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样啊  谁也不清楚赤夜的详细情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  田岛贤久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不进考现学部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越弱的狗就越想聚到一窝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田岛贤久  对团体没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说我们是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是赤夜再临的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会自己想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没礼貌的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  看起来虽然是那样  不过他是个挺温柔的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:08:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会恶心呢  反而会让大家感到羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱前辈  乱打一通是赢不了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是急躁刀路就会越乱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护结花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听上去真可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是嘴上功夫  身体却跟不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的感情没有转换成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你握着的剑寄宿着觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟就是达到悟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的感情还没有达到悟的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要训练的不是身体而是心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将感情转换成力量  只需要考虑这点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将感情转换成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到力量  能保护结花的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说出来很尴尬  不过刚才要是在战斗中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说保护结花  驱前辈都已经死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了试试驱的觉悟  我本想对她攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才他的动作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  结花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我还是弱得很丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一定会保护好结花的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉强  我也一样没有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要驱君能在我身边就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这也是为了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护结花  想把这份感情转换成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey ciao,buongiorno shiori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}你好  早上好  小栞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Piacere,come sta shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}很高兴见到你  小栞你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quanto costa？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你别用这种让人不堪入耳的意大利语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想跟拉丁的热血沸腾的归国子女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一场火热的双语恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你烧尽吧  烧成灰为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,capito
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}噢  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小栞  在欧美是女士优先的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都愿意听你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请顺着这条路一直往前走  在右转的地方去死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  乐意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}卡波那拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}注：一种美食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arrivederci  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(295,325)\fs21}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个超级笨蛋  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再笨下去我都不知道该说他什么笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花已经先过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱同学  有关昨天的修行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  现在正好在做考现学的实际操作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考现学的  实际操作？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  探索为什么结花明明是幼儿体型胸部却这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不下垂也不上挺  不用塑形胸罩就这样还真是现代奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在神圣的学园里干这种羞人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  雪子  住手  快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是贤久前辈在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我烧成灰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久前辈是念力点火能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pyrokineticist
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}操焰者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「碎片」们  今夜不会失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对即将变为残骸的罪人们  我没什么好说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无话好说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子同学  他们俩拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铇切长光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙  是用拳法的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快  草壁前辈被压制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  阿瓦利提亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能打倒古拉  这些「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须担心  这次由伊拉和因威迪亚上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有我斯佩尔比亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  前辈怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美铃前辈  不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我有力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想力量并非所有人都是期望得到才得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫去获取力量  我就是这种境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…雪子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这神速…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惊人的战斗能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个小丫头  敢小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛就像换了个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因威迪亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为「碎片」的处置交给伊拉就足够了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我统统去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的伙伴  登场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸…竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤夜要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这代价很重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再见的时候  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  结花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱…驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  明明受了那么重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞砸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一摘下眼镜就会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双重人格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人般的战斗能力和强劲的杀气  那是在哪学到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  我不太想说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  雪子  你的伤没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我会再生的  天生死不了的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我很恶心对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我习惯了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前开始大家就都觉得我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:22:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生在德拉斯贝尼亚这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是战乱和杀戮之地…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能接受我的人一共有4个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们各位  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会恶心呢  反而会让大家感到羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就算受伤了也能立刻恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复成原来的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  结花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱前辈  美铃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:22:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待着你的入部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.83,0:24:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.88,0:24:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.23,0:24:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在噩梦的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.91,0:24:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有答案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
